1
03:37:53,712 --> 03:37:55,379
Ironfoot.

2
03:37:57,883 --> 03:37:59,884
[SHOUTING]

3
03:38:06,266 --> 03:38:08,017
[ALL SHOUTING]

4
03:38:08,268 --> 03:38:09,268
[SHOUTS IN ELVISH]

5
03:38:15,525 --> 03:38:17,860
DAIN:
Hey, Thorin!

6
03:38:18,278 --> 03:38:19,695
Ironfoot has come!

7
03:38:26,870 --> 03:38:27,995
Who is that?

8
03:38:28,538 --> 03:38:29,788
He doesn't look very happy.

9
03:38:30,040 --> 03:38:32,791
It is Dain, Lord of the Iron Hills.

10
03:38:33,043 --> 03:38:34,043
Thorin's...

11
03:38:34,127 --> 03:38:35,753
- ...cousin.
- Are they alike?

12
03:38:36,838 --> 03:38:40,466
I've always found Thorin
the more reasonable of the two.

13
03:38:50,727 --> 03:38:51,852
DAIN:
Good morning.

14
03:38:52,103 --> 03:38:53,646
How are we all?

15
03:38:57,234 --> 03:38:58,609
I have a wee proposition...

16
03:38:58,860 --> 03:39:01,153
...if you wouldn't mind giving me
a few moments...

17
03:39:01,404 --> 03:39:02,655
...of your time.

18
03:39:03,907 --> 03:39:05,950
Would you consider...

19
03:39:07,953 --> 03:39:09,203
...just sodding off?

20
03:39:10,538 --> 03:39:11,538
All of you!

21
03:39:11,790 --> 03:39:13,249
Right now!

22
03:39:13,500 --> 03:39:14,500
Stand fast.

23
03:39:16,253 --> 03:39:17,503
Come now, Lord Dain.

24
03:39:18,463 --> 03:39:20,047
Gandalf the Grey.

25
03:39:21,967 --> 03:39:23,092
Tell this rabble...

26
03:39:23,343 --> 03:39:25,177
...to leave, or I'll water...

27
03:39:25,428 --> 03:39:27,096
...the ground with their blood!

28
03:39:30,600 --> 03:39:31,725
No need for war...

29
03:39:31,977 --> 03:39:34,645
...between Dwarves, Men and Elves.

30
03:39:34,896 --> 03:39:35,896
A legion of Orcs...

31
03:39:36,147 --> 03:39:37,690
...march on the Mountain.

32
03:39:37,941 --> 03:39:38,649
Stand down.

33
03:39:38,900 --> 03:39:41,944
I will not stand down before any Elf.

34
03:39:42,654 --> 03:39:45,656
Not least this faithless Woodland sprite.

35
03:39:46,658 --> 03:39:49,702
He wishes nothing but ill upon my people.

36
03:39:50,787 --> 03:39:51,787
If he chooses...

37
03:39:52,038 --> 03:39:54,707
...to stand between me and my kin...

38
03:39:56,001 --> 03:39:57,876
...I'll split his pretty head open!

39
03:40:00,213 --> 03:40:02,047
See if he's still smirking then.

40
03:40:04,259 --> 03:40:04,925
Dain...

41
03:40:05,176 --> 03:40:06,176
...wait!

42
03:40:07,554 --> 03:40:09,555
[ALL SHOUTING]

43
03:40:11,558 --> 03:40:12,558
Let them advance.

44
03:40:12,726 --> 03:40:14,560
See how far they get.

45
03:40:14,811 --> 03:40:17,062
DAIN: You think I give a dead dog
for your threats...

46
03:40:17,314 --> 03:40:19,023
...you pointy-eared...

47
03:40:19,274 --> 03:40:20,691
...princess?

48
03:40:22,027 --> 03:40:24,153
You hear that, lads? We're on!

49
03:40:24,446 --> 03:40:27,072
Let's give these bastards
a good hammering!

50
03:40:27,324 --> 03:40:28,824
[SHOUTING IN DWARVISH]

51
03:40:29,701 --> 03:40:31,493
[ALL SHOUTING]

52
03:40:31,828 --> 03:40:32,995
Stand your men down.

53
03:40:33,246 --> 03:40:35,622
I'll deal with Ironfoot and his rabble.

54
03:40:41,796 --> 03:40:42,421
Right then.

55
03:40:42,672 --> 03:40:44,506
Let's get this done.

56
03:40:45,467 --> 03:40:47,092
Send in the goats.

57
03:40:47,427 --> 03:40:49,261
[DWARF SHOUTS IN DWARVISH]

58
03:40:59,064 --> 03:41:00,647
[SHOUTING IN ELVISH]

